         Things actually change slightly at very high levels.  The mana efficiency on ToN is actualy semi decent beccause it's a Lure spell, IE never ever no matter what resisted on the majority of targets.</P><P>Also, vexing mordania is the fastest acting dot we have, and the mana/damage ratio is decent.</P><P>Plus on raids focus items make ToN nuking pretty nice for mobs under 30k hps that die faster than splurt. and other slow dots.</P><P>But you're right, necroe should alwayts be liching and tossing away hps to others and tapping them back.  I'd LOVE a shadowbond upgrade at 60.</P><P><img src="http://www.mnickey.com/zon_sig.gif" border=0><BR>-Zondro Devilldoll 60 GWARLOCK of Karana<BR>(VERY BAD)<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=21774" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=21774</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
