        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         ToN is the best nuke we have. In raids there is not enough time for DOTs to have much effect. So as much as I hate wasting half the benefit, I find myself using ToN constantly.</P><P>Of course if we are fighting undead they can be exiled and some mobs can be hit by our fire/ice nukes, but these are resisted much more often than ToN. And for 10 more mana there is always gangrenous touch.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
