         <BR>from raid perspective:</P><P>at end of "uber encounters", i usually am by 80-90% mana (it's all a matter of efficience!)<BR>but then, you just plain want to give as much as you can in order to finish off the fight asap.<BR>this is usually when i load up ToN, and hammer the mob with it till OOM. (well, considering it takes like a minute to go from FM to OOM with ToN chain casting.....) usually the mob is dead before i even get close to OOM. but i did what i was supposed to do : be damaging !</P><P>so, ToN is inefficient as for the solo/begining of fight, it then become pure good ol' nuke whenever we're getting to the end of the uber encounter.<BR><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
